#: config_translations_docs.py:53
msgid ""
"AoT is open source software designed to run on the [Raspberry "
"Pi](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raspberry_Pi) and other single-board "
"computers (SBCs). It couples inputs and outputs in interesting ways to "
"sense and manipulate the environment."
